## Educational Purpose

This software is created for educational purposes to demonstrate:
1. AI Development Workflow implementation
2. Machine Learning model integration in real-world applications
3. Point of Sale system development with AI capabilities
4. Software engineering best practices in AI projects

## Data Privacy and Ethics

This project includes synthetic data generation and fraud detection capabilities.
Any real-world implementation should consider:
- Data privacy regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
- Ethical AI practices
- Bias mitigation in machine learning models
- Transparent decision-making processes

